                                    class="pc-mtext">Room Management</span><span class="pc-arrow"><i class="ti ti-chevron-right"></i></span></a>
                                <ul class="pc-submenu">
                                    <li class="pc-item"><a class="pc-link" href="AllRooms.aspx">All Rooms</a></li>
                                    <li class="pc-item"><a class="pc-link" href="AddRoom.aspx">Add Rooms</a></li>
                                    <%--<li class="pc-item"><a class="pc-link" href="EditRoom.aspx">Update Room Details</a></li>--%>
                                    <li class="pc-item"><a class="pc-link" href="DeletedRooms.aspx">Deleted Rooms</a></li>
                                </ul>
